Interface ICreateService

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IGaCreateService, IPeCreateService
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface ICreateService
extends IPeCreateService, IGaCreateService
    The interface ICreateService provides services for the creation of all available pictogram elements and graphics algorithm's. E.g. Shapes, Connections, Rectangles, ...
